        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h1>What We Do</h1>
                    <p>SweepWell-Home Services is the company which is based in Mangalore, India. We are offering the
                        complete
                        home services including construction and renovation services, cleaning services, various repair
                        services, cleaning
                        services including plumbing and electrical repairs etc. SWeepWell Home Services delivers
                        solutions for your
                        entire home from interior to exterior.</p>
                    <p>To provide top class and hassle free home services by delivering excellent customer service.
                        We try to send our technician on time at your property and complete your query within a time
                        frame.</p>
                    <p>We have a team of well expert & educated technicians. They have more than 10 years of
                        experienced.
                        So, if you are looking for professional and well educated technician for any home related query
                        then you can trust us.</p>
                </div>
